               Confined Three Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SIMMONS. - <rs id="t18220109-102-verdict530" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-102-verdict530" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
